  "title": "How to use InstantSearch with no UI?",
  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI was wondering how Algolia’s InstantSearch operates on non webpage based applications.  My use case is to create a search experience with the [Chrome omnibox], for example to search on the [MDN].  I only care about the query, which contents comes from the omnibox, and the response, to access and display the candidates in the omnibox.  How to do that?\r\n\r\n[Chrome omnibox]: https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/omnibox\r\n[MDN]: https://developer.mozilla.org",
